Tentacles require being assigned in order to
function properly.  You have 10 tentacles
available to split between attack and defend
(and burnoff & regeneration if you have them)
To assign a tentacle to one of these functions,
type: assign tentacle # to <job>

Example -
  assign tentacle 1 to attack

To see a list of where tentacles are currently
assigned too type, 'tentacles'

Note: Burnoff and Regeneration REQUIRE
      tentacles in order to function.

Cost: 0
Skill Level: 0

